headline: Why Dividend King Nordson's Stock Popped This Week
summary: The industrial conglomerate notched convincing top- and bottom-line beats in its latest quarter.  Dividend King Nordson (NASDAQ: NDSN) was looking impressively regal on the stock market over the past few days, thanks largely to quarterly results that satisfied investors.  With that tailwind at its back, according to data compiled by S&P Global Market Intelligence, the diversified industrial conglomerate's shares finished the week almost 10% higher in price.
